------UBUNTU WEB SERVER-------
1.) Install Apache2
  sudo apt install apache2

2.) View UFW App List
  sudo ufw app list

3.) Allow Apache2 through UFW
  sudo ufw allow 'Apache'
  Options : Apache, Apache Full, Apache Secure, OpenSSH

4.) Check Status of Apache2 Service
  sudo systemctl status apache2

5.) Ensure IP Address is Hosting Apache2
    hostname -I

6.) Stopping Apache2
    sudo systemctl stop apache2

7.) Starting Apache2
    sudo systemctl start apache2

8.) Restart Apache2
    sudo systemctl restart apache2

9.) Reload Config Changes Apache2
    sudo systemctl reload apache2

10.) Disable Apache2 Startup at Boot
    sudo systemctl disable apache2

11.) Enable Apache2 Startup at Boot
    sudo systemctl enable apache2
